&lt;p&gt;Just as importantly, we&#39;ve built our internal team by investing in people. We hire individuals with the drive to succeed and provide the training, mentorship, and resources to help them build meaningful, long-term careers. Whether you&#39;re launching your career or taking the next step, ALKU is a place where growth is earned, supported, and celebrated.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re a team of competitive, collaborative, and driven professionals who believe success is built through effort, accountability, and a willingness to keep learning. At ALKU, you&#39;ll work alongside people who challenge one another to grow, celebrate wins together, and create an environment where everyone has the opportunity to make an impact.&lt;/p&gt;
